# Release Readiness Checklist

**Project:** La Última Tanda  
**Owner:** Florencia Solange Tapia  
**Release target:** Portfolio vertical slice  
**Status:** Not yet assessed

## Scope and Milestone

- [ ] All Must-have backlog items are complete.
- [ ] M5 exit criteria have been reviewed.
- [ ] No unapproved features were added after scope lock.
- [ ] Deferred items are documented.
- [ ] Known limitations are clearly communicated.

## Build Stability

- [ ] A release-candidate build has been created.
- [ ] The build launches successfully on the supported environment.
- [ ] One complete shift can be played from beginning to end.
- [ ] Restart and recovery behavior have been verified.
- [ ] Build version and creation date are documented.
- [ ] Installation and launch instructions have been tested.

## Gameplay

- [ ] Orders can be received, prepared, and delivered.
- [ ] All four vertical-slice recipes function correctly.
- [ ] Ingredient quantities update accurately.
- [ ] The shift timer starts and ends consistently.
- [ ] Both planned end-of-shift outcomes can be reached.
- [ ] Invalid actions provide understandable feedback.

